GR8 CRM is a set of [Grails|http://www.grails.org/]
plugins that makes it easy to develop web applications with CRM functionality.
With CRM we mean features like:

* Contact Management
* Task/Todo Lists
* Project and Lead Management
* Marketing and Communication

Read more about [Customer Relationship Management|http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Customer_relationship_management] on Wikipedia.
